==English==
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Orion]]'s [[belt|Belt]]'''

#{{constellation}}: A bright [[asterism]] located near the [[celestial equator]]; it consists of three bright [[star]]s lined up and visibly close together.  It is part of the [[constellation]] [[Orion]] and includes the stars [[Alnitak]] (ζ Ori), [[Alnilam]] (ε Ori), and [[Mintaka]] (δ Ori).

====Synonyms====
*the [[Saucepan]] (''Australia'')
*the [[Three Kings]], or the [[Magi]]

